title: 10 Takeaways from Week 5
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 5
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the biggest storylines following week 5 of the NFL season. The rookie quarterbacks went undefeated (1:21) while the Vikings (5:47) & Chiefs (23:18) offenses kept it rolling. Make sure to subscribe to the Move the Sticks podcast as we speed through the NFL and college football seasons.
